16192548/http://old-cdc.cma.gov.cn/shuju/search1.jsp?dsid=SURF_CLI_CHN_MUL_MMON_19712000_CES&tpcat=SURF&type=table&pageid=3\n |archivedate = 2013-10-16\n}}</ref><ref name=\"cma graphical\">\n{{cite web\n|url=http://data.cma.cn/data/weatherBk.html\n|script-title=zh:\u4e2d\u56fd\u6c14\u8c61\u6570\u636e\u7f51 - WeatherBk Data\n|publisher=[[China Meteorological Administration]]\n|accessdate=2018-11-09\n|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923231541/http://data.cma.cn/data/weatherbk.html\n|archive-date=2017-09-23\n|url-status=live\n}}\n</ref> Weather China (precipitation days 1971&ndash;2000)<ref name = \"Weather China\">\n{{cite web\n|url=http://www.weather.com.cn/cityintro/101050101.shtml?\n|script-title=zh:\u54c8\u5c14\u6ee8\u57ce\u5e02\u4ecb\u7ecd\u4ee5\u53ca\u6c14\u5019\u80cc\u666f\u5206\u6790\n|website=Weather China\n|publisher=\u4e2d\u56fd\u6c14\u8c61\u5c40\u516c\u5171\u6c14\u8c61\u670d\u52a1\u4e2d\u5fc3\n|accessdate=27 July 2013\n|language=zh-hans\n|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130630045255/http://www.weather.com.cn/cityintro/101050101.shtml\n|archive-date=30 June 2013\n|url-status=live\n|df=dmy-all\n}}\n</ref> and Weather Atlas<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.weather-atlas.com/en/china/harbin-climate|title=Harbin, China - Detailed climate information and monthly weather forecast|last=d.o.o|first=Yu Media Group|website=Weather Atlas|language=en|access-date=2019-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190709184228/https://www.weather-atlas.com/en/china/harbin-climate|archive-date=2019-07-09|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|date                    = August 2010\n}}\n\n==Administrative divisions==\nThe sub-provincial city of Harbin has direct jurisdiction over 9 [[District of China|districts]], 2 [[county-level city|county-level cities]] and 7 [[County (People's Republic of China)|counties]].\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%; margin:auto; text-align:center\"\n! colspan=12 | Map\n|-\n| colspan=12 | <div class=\"center\" style=\"position: relative\">\n{{Image label begin|image=Administrative Division Harbin.png|width={{{1|630}}}|link=}}\n{{Image label|x=280|y=680|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Daoli District|'''Daoli''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=420|y=680|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Nangang District, Harbin|'''1''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=500|y=550|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Daowai District|'''Daowai''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=460|y=730|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Pingfang District|'''2''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=360|y=510|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Songbei District|'''3''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=510|y=650|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Xiangfang District|'''4''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=480|y=360|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Hulan District|'''Hulan''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=620|y=780|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Acheng District|'''Acheng''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=120|y=830|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Shuangcheng District|'''Shuangcheng''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=1780|y=230|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Yilan County, Heilongjiang|'''Yilan<br />County''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=1370|y=570|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Fangzheng County|'''Fangzheng<br />County''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=860|y=590|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Bin County, Heilongjiang|'''Bin<br />County''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=720|y=230|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Bayan County|'''Bayan<br />County''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=990|y=270|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Mulan County|'''Mulan<br />County''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=1380|y=270|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Tonghe County|'''Tonghe<br />County''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=1220|y=760|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Yanshou County|'''Yanshou<br />County''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=1130|y=1060|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Shangzhi|'''Shangzhi<br />{{small|(city)}}''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=790|y=1220|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Wuchang, Heilongjiang|'''Wuchang<br />{{small|(city)}}''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=200|y=1200|scale={{{1|630}}}/2100|text=[[Nangang District, Harbin|'''1. Nangang''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=20